1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:08,000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

2
00:01:02,540 --> 00:01:03,220
[The Eternal Fragrance]

3
00:01:03,220 --> 00:01:07,980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

4
00:01:08,020 --> 00:01:11,140
[Episode 8]

5
00:01:11,240 --> 00:01:12,010
Spirit Slay!

6
00:01:29,270 --> 00:01:31,780
Xiuyuan!

7
00:01:39,640 --> 00:01:41,220
The suicide-for-all spell.

8
00:01:41,880 --> 00:01:43,810
I underestimated you.

9
00:01:44,470 --> 00:01:45,500
The spirit energy can't flow through.

10
00:01:50,880 --> 00:01:53,620
His spirit meridians are broken with critical internal wounds.

11
00:01:54,110 --> 00:01:56,940
The Divine Tree is his only hope to live.

12
00:01:57,160 --> 00:01:57,940
Nonsense!

13
00:01:58,360 --> 00:01:59,420
You're doomed instead.

14
00:02:01,080 --> 00:02:02,090
Worthless trash,

15
00:02:02,640 --> 00:02:04,580
die together.

16
00:02:18,200 --> 00:02:18,940
Lifei, are you alright?

17
00:02:20,710 --> 00:02:21,460
Take care of Xiuyuan.

18
00:02:22,150 --> 00:02:23,500
Since you beg for death,

19
00:02:24,390 --> 00:02:25,530
I shall oblige.

20
00:02:32,240 --> 00:02:33,900
Five Elements Merge, Demon-Subduing.

21
00:04:18,030 --> 00:04:19,060
Pointless struggle.

22
00:04:19,830 --> 00:04:22,770
Villain, Mr. Zuo Qiu won't spare you.

23
00:04:24,960 --> 00:04:26,690
When I find the Divine Tree,

24
00:04:27,030 --> 00:04:28,660
I'll fear no one.

25
00:04:50,760 --> 00:04:52,370
Such surging spirit energy.

26
00:05:05,520 --> 00:05:06,450
Finally, you revealed yourself.

27
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:08,890
If you'd been any later, we'd have been dead.

28
00:05:09,150 --> 00:05:10,210
My wounds haven't fully healed,

29
00:05:10,350 --> 00:05:11,540
yet I had to save you.

30
00:05:11,880 --> 00:05:13,300
Do you know how much cultivation I lost?

31
00:05:13,880 --> 00:05:14,420
I'm going to rest.

32
00:05:14,830 --> 00:05:15,980
Don't come to me in a year or half a year.

33
00:05:16,590 --> 00:05:18,210
Wait, please save Xiuyuan!

34
00:05:18,710 --> 00:05:20,450
His meridians are shattered, and his spirit root is ruined.

35
00:05:20,880 --> 00:05:21,500
There's nothing I can do.

36
00:05:21,830 --> 00:05:22,770
Let fate take its course.

37
00:05:23,590 --> 00:05:24,500
What?

38
00:05:25,230 --> 00:05:27,060
No, he mustn't die!

39
00:05:27,390 --> 00:05:28,130
Save him.

40
00:05:28,910 --> 00:05:30,770
Save him, please.

41
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:32,740
Head to Qingqiu.

42
00:05:33,200 --> 00:05:35,180
The Ganhua Realm holds what can heal him.

43
00:05:35,830 --> 00:05:36,690
Qingqiu?

44
00:05:37,590 --> 00:05:38,060
Wait.

45
00:05:39,710 --> 00:05:40,370
Where

46
00:05:40,880 --> 00:05:42,980
is the Ganhua Realm, Riyan?

47
00:05:48,470 --> 00:05:49,250
You mustn't die!

48
00:05:51,000 --> 00:05:51,740
I'll save you.

49
00:05:58,710 --> 00:06:00,100
Xiuyuan!

50
00:06:02,640 --> 00:06:03,210
Lifei.

51
00:06:04,760 --> 00:06:05,300
Xiuyuan.

52
00:06:07,080 --> 00:06:07,660
What's wrong with him?

53
00:06:09,390 --> 00:06:10,100
Let's hurry back to the academy.

54
00:06:12,150 --> 00:06:13,130
Don't bother.

55
00:06:15,150 --> 00:06:15,810
Mr. Hu.

56
00:06:16,440 --> 00:06:17,420
Find a place to bury him.

57
00:06:18,880 --> 00:06:19,620
If you won't save him, I will.

58
00:06:21,390 --> 00:06:23,130
Head back to Qingqiu. I have a way to heal him.

59
00:06:23,150 --> 00:06:24,420
I'm coming with you. Go.

60
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:27,330
Mr. Hu, Xiuyuan is on the brink of death.

61
00:06:28,200 --> 00:06:29,620
We'll take him to Qingqiu.

62
00:06:30,230 --> 00:06:31,500
Once things calm down,

63
00:06:31,830 --> 00:06:33,250
we'll go to the academy to plead guilty.

64
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:34,620
We beg for your permission.

65
00:06:38,120 --> 00:06:39,420
One's fate is predetermined.

66
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:43,010
What if you fail to save him?

67
00:06:44,230 --> 00:06:45,010
As his classmates,

68
00:06:45,270 --> 00:06:47,330
we should stand together through hardship and do our best.

69
00:06:48,080 --> 00:06:49,740
If we get expelled from the academy for this,

70
00:06:50,200 --> 00:06:51,250
we'll accept it without regret.

71
00:06:52,030 --> 00:06:52,500
Yes.

72
00:06:53,790 --> 00:06:54,330
That's right.

73
00:07:04,150 --> 00:07:04,660
Xiuyuan!

74
00:07:04,760 --> 00:07:05,180
Xiuyuan!

75
00:07:05,790 --> 00:07:06,570
What are you doing?

76
00:07:09,910 --> 00:07:12,740
Lifei, Mr. Hu is saving him.

77
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:19,690
I've stabilized his heart meridians for now.

78
00:07:20,390 --> 00:07:22,180
He won‘t be dead in at least three stays,

79
00:07:23,150 --> 00:07:25,890
but what happens later depends on his fate.

80
00:07:27,030 --> 00:07:29,100
I'll cover for you with the academy.

81
00:07:29,520 --> 00:07:31,770
Bring him back safe once you cure him.

82
00:07:32,470 --> 00:07:35,010
You shouldn't stay outside alone.

83
00:07:40,270 --> 00:07:41,500
What does he mean?

84
00:07:42,200 --> 00:07:43,660
Is he going to cover for us?

85
00:07:44,150 --> 00:07:45,860
Never mind. Save Xiuyuan first.

86
00:07:49,590 --> 00:07:50,100
Let's go.

87
00:08:09,270 --> 00:08:09,890
Your Highness,

88
00:08:10,350 --> 00:08:11,890
your cultivation is astonishing now.

89
00:08:12,320 --> 00:08:13,330
Like our teachers,

90
00:08:13,880 --> 00:08:15,450
you can weave a spirit energy barrier for healing.

91
00:08:16,350 --> 00:08:17,540
The Zhurong Stone is powerful.

92
00:08:18,000 --> 00:08:19,690
It can sustain spirit energy,

93
00:08:20,120 --> 00:08:21,500
barely enough to last for a few hours.

94
00:08:22,590 --> 00:08:25,060
A few hours? Exactly how long?

95
00:08:25,150 --> 00:08:25,890
Don't worry.

96
00:08:27,230 --> 00:08:28,500
Xiuyuan is out of immediate danger.

97
00:08:29,270 --> 00:08:30,180
Stay here and look after him.

98
00:08:30,760 --> 00:08:32,420
We'll search for the Ganhua Realm.

99
00:08:33,280 --> 00:08:34,090
I can search.

100
00:08:35,560 --> 00:08:37,810
Lifei, your spirit power is faint,

101
00:08:38,110 --> 00:08:39,730
and you've channeled energy to Xiuyuan nonstop.

102
00:08:40,230 --> 00:08:41,660
You can barely stand right now.

103
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:42,570
Yeah.

104
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:44,660
There's plenty of medicinal herbs here.

105
00:08:45,280 --> 00:08:47,330
Lifei, boil some nourishing medicine.

106
00:08:47,470 --> 00:08:48,380
We'll be back soon.

107
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:53,210
Qingqiu's mountains are steep, filled with spirits,

108
00:08:53,590 --> 00:08:54,730
but most mean no harm.

109
00:08:55,110 --> 00:08:56,540
If you run into trouble,

110
00:08:57,230 --> 00:08:58,690
tell them you're Xiaobangchui's friends.

111
00:08:59,280 --> 00:08:59,810
Stay safe.

112
00:09:01,110 --> 00:09:01,540
Okay.

113
00:09:18,800 --> 00:09:20,730
When my master and I traveled,

114
00:09:21,320 --> 00:09:24,090
we lodged in inns with money, and shrines without.

115
00:09:25,680 --> 00:09:27,260
After coming back to Qingqiu,

116
00:09:29,280 --> 00:09:30,940
we spent two to three months

117
00:09:31,040 --> 00:09:32,690
rebuilding this wooden house.

118
00:09:33,560 --> 00:09:35,020
This is our only home.

119
00:09:35,040 --> 00:09:36,300
No outsiders have set foot here.

120
00:09:37,230 --> 00:09:38,810
You're our first visitor,

121
00:09:39,230 --> 00:09:41,940
but look at you, bedridden as soon as you arrived.

122
00:09:57,590 --> 00:09:58,730
Are you crazy?

123
00:09:59,630 --> 00:10:01,570
Why risk your life saving me time and again?

124
00:10:11,710 --> 00:10:12,780
Giving up saving Shanhua?

125
00:10:16,470 --> 00:10:17,940
Why treat me so well?

126
00:10:38,350 --> 00:10:41,660
My master said never owe anyone a favor.

127
00:10:43,110 --> 00:10:45,570
I'll help rescue Shanhua

128
00:10:46,560 --> 00:10:48,380
once you recover, okay?

129
00:11:01,920 --> 00:11:02,610
Found nothing?

130
00:11:04,830 --> 00:11:06,540
We searched every spirit spot

131
00:11:06,560 --> 00:11:07,180
across Qingqiu,

132
00:11:07,750 --> 00:11:09,730
yet sensed no spot with strange spirit energy.

133
00:11:11,630 --> 00:11:14,180
Lifei, living here ages,

134
00:11:14,630 --> 00:11:15,940
don't you know the Ganhua Realm?

135
00:11:20,200 --> 00:11:21,260
Who told you about it?

136
00:11:22,080 --> 00:11:23,330
Does the Ganhua Realm truly exist?

137
00:11:27,920 --> 00:11:28,780
Speak up.

138
00:11:33,110 --> 00:11:33,940
As a hidden secret realm,

139
00:11:34,200 --> 00:11:35,140
it can't be easily

140
00:11:35,160 --> 00:11:36,090
tracked down.

141
00:11:38,680 --> 00:11:40,730
Alright. I'll search tomorrow morning again.

142
00:11:42,160 --> 00:11:43,210
But Mr. Hu warned

143
00:11:43,990 --> 00:11:45,140
that Xiuyuan only has three days to live.

144
00:11:45,470 --> 00:11:47,180
A day and a half have passed, and you...

145
00:11:50,920 --> 00:11:51,490
Xiuyuan!

146
00:11:52,560 --> 00:11:53,060
Xiuyuan!

147
00:12:12,710 --> 00:12:13,610
I'm going out to search now.

148
00:12:15,590 --> 00:12:16,140
Lifei.

149
00:12:31,350 --> 00:12:33,380
None of you know where the Ganhua Realm is.

150
00:12:35,830 --> 00:12:36,450
Wait.

151
00:12:49,160 --> 00:12:49,970
Tell

152
00:12:49,990 --> 00:12:51,780
every spirit and monster you can find

153
00:12:52,110 --> 00:12:53,380
that I'll offer anything

154
00:12:56,040 --> 00:12:57,140
in exchange for clues.

155
00:13:05,870 --> 00:13:06,450
Lifei.

156
00:13:10,110 --> 00:13:11,260
Your spirit power is long exhausted.

157
00:13:11,710 --> 00:13:13,940
Keep this up, and you'll collapse next.

158
00:13:14,960 --> 00:13:15,660
Tongzhou,

159
00:13:16,510 --> 00:13:18,540
what if the Ganhua Realm isn't real?

160
00:13:21,960 --> 00:13:23,260
Who told you

161
00:13:24,110 --> 00:13:25,330
it can save Xiuyuan?

162
00:13:26,200 --> 00:13:28,260
My friend.

163
00:13:29,920 --> 00:13:32,730
But what if I misheard?

164
00:13:33,510 --> 00:13:34,850
What if we never find it?

165
00:13:35,470 --> 00:13:36,780
Will Xiuyuan die?

166
00:13:40,320 --> 00:13:41,300
We'll find it for sure.

167
00:13:42,230 --> 00:13:44,610
We can use herbs, channel spirit energy,

168
00:13:45,160 --> 00:13:46,490
and try every possible means

169
00:13:47,350 --> 00:13:48,020
to save him.

170
00:13:53,320 --> 00:13:54,690
You're just comforting me.

171
00:13:55,630 --> 00:13:56,300
I don't need empty words.

172
00:13:57,400 --> 00:13:58,260
Only one day left.

173
00:13:59,800 --> 00:14:00,610
I'll find it.

174
00:14:02,160 --> 00:14:03,810
I'll definitely locate the Ganhua Realm.

175
00:14:06,040 --> 00:14:06,610
Lifei.

176
00:14:21,680 --> 00:14:22,940
I picked some healing herbs

177
00:14:23,960 --> 00:14:25,090
for Xiuyuan.

178
00:14:33,280 --> 00:14:33,900
Changyue.

179
00:14:37,440 --> 00:14:38,060
Xiuyuan!

180
00:14:39,710 --> 00:14:40,330
Xiuyuan!

181
00:14:43,200 --> 00:14:44,260
His pulse is far too faint.

182
00:14:44,750 --> 00:14:45,850
He was supposed to last another day.

183
00:15:22,630 --> 00:15:23,970
I'll offer anything

184
00:15:25,560 --> 00:15:26,610
for clues.

185
00:15:30,960 --> 00:15:32,610
Those spirits crave my blood.

186
00:15:34,350 --> 00:15:36,940
Yeah. My blood might work.

187
00:15:45,350 --> 00:15:45,970
Drink it.

188
00:15:52,750 --> 00:15:55,020
Drink it.

189
00:15:55,870 --> 00:15:56,850
Drink it.

190
00:16:06,510 --> 00:16:07,140
Xiuyuan.

191
00:16:12,870 --> 00:16:16,210
Xiuyuan.

192
00:16:30,350 --> 00:16:32,850
Stay awake! Open your eyes!

193
00:16:51,470 --> 00:16:52,180
Lei Xiuyuan!

194
00:17:01,230 --> 00:17:02,180
This won't do.

195
00:17:02,440 --> 00:17:03,450
Is there any other way?

196
00:17:03,750 --> 00:17:05,250
Lifei!

197
00:17:38,160 --> 00:17:40,580
Essence and Qi form the Core.  Take the Inner Core out of the body…

198
00:17:41,640 --> 00:17:42,530
The Ten Forbidden Arts of Sorcerers.

199
00:17:44,270 --> 00:17:44,860
What's this?

200
00:17:47,440 --> 00:17:49,620
An Inner Core? Can you just take it out?

201
00:17:50,120 --> 00:17:50,770
To save him,

202
00:17:51,270 --> 00:17:52,730
you'd believe any crooked forbidden trick?

203
00:17:52,750 --> 00:17:53,620
Are you throwing your life away?

204
00:17:53,840 --> 00:17:55,180
You want to trade your life for Xiuyuan's,

205
00:17:55,710 --> 00:17:56,940
but he would never allow it.

206
00:18:01,790 --> 00:18:04,770
Nothing works,

207
00:18:05,750 --> 00:18:07,340
but the three days will be up soon.

208
00:18:08,120 --> 00:18:09,210
What can we do?

209
00:18:14,920 --> 00:18:16,100
Qingqiu swarms with spirits,

210
00:18:16,640 --> 00:18:17,940
so ordinary people cannot dwell here.

211
00:18:18,840 --> 00:18:20,770
Your master kept you safe here all these years,

212
00:18:21,200 --> 00:18:22,340
so he must be a hidden expert.

213
00:18:23,270 --> 00:18:24,770
Did he ever mention

214
00:18:25,400 --> 00:18:26,210
healing herbs

215
00:18:27,230 --> 00:18:28,210
or any special land?

216
00:18:29,550 --> 00:18:32,010
[Young Lifei]
Xiaobangchui, don't worry.

217
00:18:32,030 --> 00:18:33,730
I'll find a way to heal you.

218
00:18:39,510 --> 00:18:40,580
I remember now.

219
00:18:49,510 --> 00:18:50,580
It's right over there,

220
00:18:51,470 --> 00:18:52,860
but I can't recall the entrance.

221
00:18:53,160 --> 00:18:54,820
If the Ganhua Realm holds mysterious power,

222
00:18:55,120 --> 00:18:56,340
its terrain must carry clues.

223
00:18:57,030 --> 00:18:58,820
My master always said yin and yang coexist.

224
00:18:59,070 --> 00:19:00,770
The void is substance; emptiness is fullness.

225
00:19:02,400 --> 00:19:02,900
Be careful.

226
00:19:07,840 --> 00:19:08,450
Let's check it down there.

227
00:19:15,840 --> 00:19:16,730
Stars?

228
00:19:19,510 --> 00:19:20,530
These look like islands.

229
00:19:21,790 --> 00:19:24,010
Legends say thousands of isles lie beyond the sea,

230
00:19:25,200 --> 00:19:27,140
yet there are far more here than that.

231
00:19:34,360 --> 00:19:35,450
Testing each one

232
00:19:36,200 --> 00:19:37,420
would take a whole day.

233
00:19:38,840 --> 00:19:40,970
Dawn draws near; Xiuyuan can't wait that long.

234
00:19:41,310 --> 00:19:42,050
Try them now.

235
00:20:04,510 --> 00:20:05,940
Lifei.

236
00:20:06,510 --> 00:20:07,940
Let me do it, Lifei.

237
00:20:09,880 --> 00:20:10,580
Lifei.

238
00:21:07,100 --> 00:21:10,480
[Ganhua Realm]

239
00:21:39,920 --> 00:21:40,690
You see that?

240
00:21:41,680 --> 00:21:42,340
What?

241
00:21:42,600 --> 00:21:43,340
It lights up!

242
00:22:04,640 --> 00:22:05,450
I got it now.

243
00:22:06,840 --> 00:22:07,490
This is the one.

244
00:22:18,360 --> 00:22:19,770
I'll do it myself. Keep watch nearby.

245
00:22:44,750 --> 00:22:48,340
Immense spirit power! Could it be this round stone?

246
00:22:56,900 --> 00:23:00,580
♪I trade all the mortal world's splendor♪

247
00:23:00,900 --> 00:23:02,200
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

248
00:23:02,200 --> 00:23:03,010
Hold on!

249
00:23:03,860 --> 00:23:07,180
♪Our fates intertwined, embracing yet fighting♪

250
00:23:07,420 --> 00:23:09,620
♪The hardest bond to balance♪

251
00:23:10,660 --> 00:23:14,140
♪Obsessed and struggling, a thousand thoughts arise♪

252
00:23:14,860 --> 00:23:17,220
♪Love sprouts again in this lifetime♪

253
00:23:17,820 --> 00:23:19,340
♪No calamity can rival♪

254
00:23:19,740 --> 00:23:22,780
♪the lingering thread of a fragrance♪

255
00:23:24,920 --> 00:23:28,400
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

256
00:23:29,160 --> 00:23:31,400
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

257
00:23:31,840 --> 00:23:34,880
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge, past the pagoda♪

258
00:23:35,960 --> 00:23:36,730
This spirit power…

259
00:23:36,730 --> 00:23:37,800
♪In fine robes on galloping horses♪

260
00:23:38,600 --> 00:23:42,080
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

261
00:23:42,440 --> 00:23:44,720
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

262
00:23:45,240 --> 00:23:48,200
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign♪

263
00:23:48,920 --> 00:23:51,120
♪Supreme♪

264
00:23:52,200 --> 00:23:55,730
♪If the seal can't be broken, then let it go♪

265
00:23:56,400 --> 00:23:58,770
♪Where the heart finds peace, there is home♪

266
00:23:59,090 --> 00:24:02,290
♪Side by side, we fly through seas of clouds, break through the waves♪

267
00:24:02,890 --> 00:24:05,170
♪The heart's ocean knows no shore♪

268
00:24:05,570 --> 00:24:09,290
♪Always, at the very end of fate♪

269
00:24:09,930 --> 00:24:12,330
♪Comes that one moment of defiance♪

270
00:24:12,770 --> 00:24:15,930
♪In the human world or above, like flowing water♪

271
00:24:16,530 --> 00:24:18,890
♪And falling petals♪

272
00:24:19,610 --> 00:24:23,880
♪Let this fleeting life be whatever it may♪

273
00:24:28,030 --> 00:24:28,620
Lifei.

274
00:24:29,440 --> 00:24:30,010
Xiuyuan.

275
00:24:54,160 --> 00:24:54,900
Xiuyuan.

276
00:24:57,230 --> 00:24:59,340
You're awake, Lifei.

277
00:25:02,230 --> 00:25:04,210
What about Xiuyuan? Is he alright?

278
00:25:04,710 --> 00:25:06,290
He's safe.

279
00:25:06,640 --> 00:25:07,290
Calm down.

280
00:25:07,510 --> 00:25:08,490
You've been asleep for three days.

281
00:25:09,270 --> 00:25:10,100
Three days?

282
00:25:11,160 --> 00:25:12,420
Xiuyuan, be careful.

283
00:25:30,310 --> 00:25:31,100
Xiuyuan.

284
00:25:41,750 --> 00:25:44,710
♪When fate calls, I rise as a worthy one♪

285
00:25:44,830 --> 00:25:47,470
♪I'll never back down♪

286
00:25:47,510 --> 00:25:53,010
♪I keep my former fearless resolve, never return it♪

287
00:25:53,730 --> 00:25:57,490
♪Dusk till dawn, I stay awake♪

288
00:25:57,610 --> 00:26:00,570
♪Bearing heavy missions, I ride far away♪

289
00:26:01,840 --> 00:26:02,730
Really healed?

290
00:26:03,310 --> 00:26:04,250
Fully mended?

291
00:26:04,710 --> 00:26:07,180
Yes, I've checked thoroughly.

292
00:26:07,640 --> 00:26:08,620
His broken meridians are reconnected.

293
00:26:09,120 --> 00:26:11,180
The Ganhua Realm is truly a miraculous place.

294
00:26:12,030 --> 00:26:14,940
That's just wonderful.

295
00:26:14,940 --> 00:26:17,200
♪Ambition surges; we hold new feasts amid thorns♪

296
00:26:17,200 --> 00:26:18,100
You have no idea

297
00:26:18,750 --> 00:26:20,250
how badly you are hurt.

298
00:26:21,710 --> 00:26:22,530
Never

299
00:26:23,550 --> 00:26:24,940
use that suicide-for-all spell

300
00:26:25,230 --> 00:26:26,290
again.

301
00:26:26,510 --> 00:26:27,820
I was terrified.

302
00:26:37,680 --> 00:26:38,380
I won't.

303
00:26:40,310 --> 00:26:42,530
You'd better keep your word.

304
00:26:43,360 --> 00:26:44,250
If you try it

305
00:26:45,510 --> 00:26:46,180
again…

306
00:26:47,330 --> 00:26:49,930
♪Bearing heavy missions, I ride far away♪

307
00:26:50,130 --> 00:26:54,730
♪The hidden fire in my heart forges a massive sword♪

308
00:26:55,010 --> 00:26:59,410
♪With you, we climb bleak cliffs beneath endless gloom♪

309
00:26:59,410 --> 00:27:01,470
♪Bow our heads and endure bitter gales♪

310
00:27:01,470 --> 00:27:03,580
Promise you'll never sacrifice yourself for me.

311
00:27:03,580 --> 00:27:07,330
♪Ambition surges; we hold new feasts amid thorns♪

312
00:27:07,680 --> 00:27:11,560
♪Climb high, lone sword sings, dance beneath autumn moon♪

313
00:27:11,760 --> 00:27:13,920
♪Dreams wane, then bloom full soon♪

314
00:27:14,080 --> 00:27:19,680
♪Rough the road, yet my steps shall never cease to move♪

315
00:27:20,060 --> 00:27:23,680
♪Banners wave, war drums thunder across the sky♪

316
00:27:23,800 --> 00:27:26,110
♪I tread fleeting mist beneath my feet♪

317
00:27:26,280 --> 00:27:32,000
♪At last I see, life's end lies boundless wild free♪

318
00:27:35,510 --> 00:27:36,690
Alright.

319
00:27:39,360 --> 00:27:41,180
Survive hardship, and good luck awaits.

320
00:27:43,790 --> 00:27:45,620
Here, a bowl each.

321
00:27:46,200 --> 00:27:47,050
Cry after drinking.

322
00:27:48,680 --> 00:27:49,250
True that.

323
00:27:49,470 --> 00:27:51,210
Survive hardship, and good luck awaits. Here.

324
00:27:53,160 --> 00:27:53,820
A bowl each.

325
00:27:55,400 --> 00:27:55,970
Drink it all.

326
00:29:54,640 --> 00:29:56,250
The strange spirit aura of the tower.

327
00:29:58,920 --> 00:29:59,620
The Divine Tree.

328
00:30:03,550 --> 00:30:04,660
You know, over there.

329
00:30:05,030 --> 00:30:06,660
The mushrooms there are the best.

330
00:30:07,120 --> 00:30:08,140
I gather them

331
00:30:08,270 --> 00:30:09,660
after every rain.

332
00:30:10,230 --> 00:30:12,820
Sometimes, I caught rabbits

333
00:30:13,400 --> 00:30:15,530
to stew with mushrooms.

334
00:30:19,310 --> 00:30:20,530
Qingqiu is such a nice land.

335
00:30:22,310 --> 00:30:23,250
Do you like it?

336
00:30:26,360 --> 00:30:27,770
Then live here together with me.

337
00:30:35,270 --> 00:30:36,970
Together?

338
00:30:39,030 --> 00:30:39,690
Look.

339
00:30:39,840 --> 00:30:41,660
You said your wish

340
00:30:41,680 --> 00:30:43,140
is to live peacefully with Shanhua.

341
00:30:43,600 --> 00:30:45,100
Qingqiu is such a vast land.

342
00:30:45,710 --> 00:30:47,580
Once you rescue Shanhua

343
00:30:47,990 --> 00:30:49,010
and I find my master,

344
00:30:49,360 --> 00:30:50,690
we can come back together.

345
00:30:51,440 --> 00:30:52,140
Then

346
00:30:53,600 --> 00:30:54,250
we'll build

347
00:30:54,990 --> 00:30:56,250
a house right there,

348
00:30:56,550 --> 00:30:59,690
and grow radishes in the yard.

349
00:31:34,750 --> 00:31:37,210
Hey, let me introduce.

350
00:31:37,470 --> 00:31:40,380
This is Lei Xiuyuan, my best friend.

351
00:31:49,550 --> 00:31:51,140
Your surging spirit energy

352
00:31:51,360 --> 00:31:52,250
has intimidated them.

353
00:31:52,990 --> 00:31:53,340
I…

354
00:31:54,200 --> 00:31:56,940
Don't be scared.

355
00:31:57,310 --> 00:31:58,970
He is one of us.

356
00:32:25,470 --> 00:32:26,900
Qingqiu swarms with bugs and mosquitoes.

357
00:32:26,990 --> 00:32:28,100
They grow more venomous as autumn comes.

358
00:32:28,840 --> 00:32:30,970
Smoke the room, and you'll sleep soundly tonight.

359
00:32:35,470 --> 00:32:36,100
Are you alright?

360
00:32:36,680 --> 00:32:37,180
I'm fine.

361
00:32:39,990 --> 00:32:41,820
This is my master's treasure chest.

362
00:32:53,750 --> 00:32:55,100
Records of Overseas Legends.

363
00:32:56,960 --> 00:32:58,900
You can read these weird characters?

364
00:32:59,880 --> 00:33:02,180
I snuck peeks before, but couldn't understand.

365
00:33:06,120 --> 00:33:07,770
How did I learn these characters?

366
00:33:16,750 --> 00:33:17,490
What's this?

367
00:33:21,360 --> 00:33:23,690
Mostly legends of overseas lands.

368
00:33:26,160 --> 00:33:28,860
Beyond the East Sea's Ruins live exotic monster clans,

369
00:33:29,550 --> 00:33:32,380
their skin pitch-black and twin serpents coiled in their hands.

370
00:33:34,270 --> 00:33:35,450
How incredible.

371
00:33:38,400 --> 00:33:41,050
Could my master have planned to live overseas?

372
00:33:44,030 --> 00:33:44,970
As a sorcerer,

373
00:33:45,960 --> 00:33:48,340
he lived safely in spirit-infested Qingqiu,

374
00:33:49,600 --> 00:33:52,180
while hiding from the world, concealing his identity,

375
00:33:52,640 --> 00:33:53,770
and knowing all about overseas lands.

376
00:33:55,310 --> 00:33:55,970
Who exactly

377
00:33:57,310 --> 00:33:58,250
is he?

378
00:34:02,990 --> 00:34:04,420
The Mid-autumn Festival is almost here.

379
00:34:04,550 --> 00:34:06,180
Why hasn't Tongzhou come back yet?

380
00:34:07,920 --> 00:34:08,940
Our teacher told you

381
00:34:09,440 --> 00:34:11,450
that Mr. Zuo sent him to visit a master.

382
00:34:12,190 --> 00:34:12,740
In this world,

383
00:34:12,760 --> 00:34:14,570
there can't be many masters

384
00:34:14,590 --> 00:34:15,610
stronger than Mr. Xuanshan.

385
00:34:16,110 --> 00:34:18,050
Besides, why can Lifei go,

386
00:34:18,070 --> 00:34:19,300
but I'm not allowed to go along?

387
00:34:20,320 --> 00:34:20,900
Well…

388
00:34:22,880 --> 00:34:24,090
Youran,

389
00:34:25,760 --> 00:34:26,780
do you know

390
00:34:26,800 --> 00:34:27,740
when Tongzhou will return?

391
00:34:28,720 --> 00:34:31,450
The master thought they were outstanding talents,

392
00:34:31,470 --> 00:34:32,570
so he kept them for a few extra days.

393
00:34:34,150 --> 00:34:36,490
A master? What master?

394
00:34:36,670 --> 00:34:38,420
What's his name? Which sect does he belong to?

395
00:34:39,360 --> 00:34:41,490
A true master's identity is never to be revealed.

396
00:34:43,400 --> 00:34:44,050
Master.

397
00:34:46,440 --> 00:34:49,090
This chicken is acting weird today.

398
00:34:50,030 --> 00:34:52,450
If you don't tell me the truth,

399
00:34:52,510 --> 00:34:54,050
I'll pluck all its feathers out.

400
00:34:54,070 --> 00:34:55,940
Wait. Don't be rash!

401
00:34:55,990 --> 00:34:57,010
Calm down, please!

402
00:34:57,030 --> 00:34:58,010
Don't act recklessly.

403
00:34:58,030 --> 00:34:59,220
Calm down?

404
00:34:59,920 --> 00:35:01,170
I'm really going to pluck it.

405
00:35:01,720 --> 00:35:02,220
Your Ladyship.

406
00:35:03,070 --> 00:35:03,570
Your Ladyship.

407
00:35:04,800 --> 00:35:05,490
Your Ladyship.

408
00:35:05,880 --> 00:35:07,490
It bit me!

409
00:35:07,510 --> 00:35:07,970
Your Ladyship.

410
00:35:07,990 --> 00:35:10,090
A mere chicken dares to attack me!

411
00:35:10,720 --> 00:35:12,260
I told you to calm down.

412
00:35:13,630 --> 00:35:15,130
So young yet so fiery,

413
00:35:15,400 --> 00:35:16,570
you may not grow taller.

414
00:35:17,440 --> 00:35:18,300
Are you alright?

415
00:35:19,240 --> 00:35:20,010
Lifei, let me handle this.

416
00:35:20,670 --> 00:35:21,300
Be careful.

417
00:35:23,190 --> 00:35:24,010
Come on, let's eat.

418
00:35:24,800 --> 00:35:26,970
I'll show you my signature dishes.

419
00:35:27,400 --> 00:35:30,050
This is Nectar Radish Soup.

420
00:35:30,880 --> 00:35:31,650
This exquisite carving

421
00:35:32,720 --> 00:35:35,530
is Fortune Rolling Radish.

422
00:35:37,240 --> 00:35:38,570
When I have time, I'll make my ultimate specialty

423
00:35:38,840 --> 00:35:41,340
that goes perfectly with three steamed buns at a go.

424
00:35:41,760 --> 00:35:42,420
What?

425
00:35:42,630 --> 00:35:43,300
What's that?

426
00:35:43,990 --> 00:35:44,700
What is it?

427
00:35:45,550 --> 00:35:47,220
Marinated radish and soy pickled radish.

428
00:35:52,470 --> 00:35:54,220
Now I get why your master

429
00:35:54,240 --> 00:35:55,610
called you Xiaobangchui.

430
00:35:55,920 --> 00:35:58,050
These radishes look just like mallets.

431
00:35:58,510 --> 00:36:00,570
No, my master called me Xiaobangchui

432
00:36:00,960 --> 00:36:02,740
because when he found me by the river,

433
00:36:02,760 --> 00:36:04,130
a young woman was beating clothes

434
00:36:04,510 --> 00:36:05,780
with a wooden mallet.

435
00:36:05,800 --> 00:36:07,090
She was breathtakingly beautiful.

436
00:36:07,470 --> 00:36:08,610
My master wanted to remember her,

437
00:36:08,630 --> 00:36:09,860
so he called me Xiaobangchui.

438
00:36:12,670 --> 00:36:13,420
That story fits well.

439
00:36:25,470 --> 00:36:27,650
Lifei, do you have any other kin?

440
00:36:28,280 --> 00:36:30,450
I do, six of them.

441
00:36:31,070 --> 00:36:32,130
Where are they?

442
00:36:33,030 --> 00:36:35,260
One is my senior brother, whom I've never met.

443
00:36:35,550 --> 00:36:36,970
I have no clue where he is.

444
00:36:38,280 --> 00:36:39,490
As for the other five,

445
00:36:39,630 --> 00:36:40,740
they're right here with me.

446
00:36:56,280 --> 00:36:57,380
My master once said

447
00:36:57,550 --> 00:36:59,530
that in the restless world, people are unfeeling.

448
00:36:59,880 --> 00:37:01,450
Most only chase luck and flee misfortune.

449
00:37:02,110 --> 00:37:04,860
A person who treats you faithfully amid hardship

450
00:37:05,030 --> 00:37:07,170
and stands by you unto death surpasses your family.

451
00:37:11,030 --> 00:37:11,780
Lifei is right.

452
00:37:12,760 --> 00:37:13,970
From this day on,

453
00:37:14,280 --> 00:37:16,420
we're like family, bound as siblings.

454
00:37:16,670 --> 00:37:17,970
Yes, family.

455
00:37:25,720 --> 00:37:26,820
Since we're one family,

456
00:37:27,320 --> 00:37:31,300
I have a truth to confess to you today.

457
00:37:53,150 --> 00:37:56,970
I am the Crown Prince of Gaolu,

458
00:37:58,550 --> 00:38:01,260
whom Zong Quan has long sought to wipe out entirely.

459
00:38:17,550 --> 00:38:18,420
Over the years,

460
00:38:20,110 --> 00:38:20,940
Xiuyuan has endured

461
00:38:22,190 --> 00:38:23,380
all the suffering for me.

462
00:38:31,470 --> 00:38:33,650
States across the Central Plains have waged wars for a hundred years.

463
00:38:34,240 --> 00:38:35,450
For every key imperial heir,

464
00:38:35,960 --> 00:38:37,090
a child of the same age

465
00:38:37,440 --> 00:38:39,090
is arranged from childhood

466
00:38:39,110 --> 00:38:39,820
as their body double.

467
00:38:41,190 --> 00:38:43,650
Xiuyuan must be Ye Ye's double.

468
00:38:49,320 --> 00:38:50,170
No blame falls on Ye Ye.

469
00:38:51,320 --> 00:38:53,610
Such imperial secrets are hard to speak aloud.

470
00:38:54,990 --> 00:38:56,260
Yet Xiuyuan bore the harder lot.

471
00:38:56,840 --> 00:38:59,170
Facing death time and again, he never revealed his true identity.

472
00:39:02,920 --> 00:39:04,650
Xiuyuan, I am sorry.

473
00:39:05,070 --> 00:39:06,340
Had I told the truth earlier,

474
00:39:06,720 --> 00:39:08,420
Zong Quan wouldn't have hunted you relentlessly.

475
00:39:08,470 --> 00:39:08,900
I…

476
00:39:08,920 --> 00:39:11,740
What he's done has nothing to do with you.

477
00:39:23,030 --> 00:39:23,610
Ye Ye,

478
00:39:25,800 --> 00:39:26,900
we have survived all the horrors,

479
00:39:28,440 --> 00:39:30,700
so let us not dwell on the past.

480
00:39:31,240 --> 00:39:31,900
Xiuyuan.

481
00:39:32,240 --> 00:39:35,340
We've grown up, and we're all still alive.

482
00:39:36,670 --> 00:39:37,420
That is enough.

483
00:39:39,150 --> 00:39:41,220
You're right, no more looking back.

484
00:39:41,440 --> 00:39:42,530
We must march forward.

485
00:39:42,990 --> 00:39:43,650
Look at us now.

486
00:39:43,960 --> 00:39:45,650
We're all here together like a family.

487
00:39:45,670 --> 00:39:47,050
We have food to eat and a school to attend.

488
00:39:48,110 --> 00:39:48,970
Dig in, quick!

489
00:39:48,990 --> 00:39:50,860
My radish soup has gone cold. Come on.

490
00:39:54,360 --> 00:39:54,820
This

491
00:39:56,240 --> 00:39:57,940
God of Wealth statue is definitely for Tongzhou.

492
00:40:04,190 --> 00:40:04,780
Alright.

493
00:40:05,150 --> 00:40:06,940
If you ask of me, whatever I possess,

494
00:40:07,360 --> 00:40:08,300
I'll give every last bit to you.

495
00:40:10,360 --> 00:40:12,220
No surprise they call you cash...

496
00:40:17,550 --> 00:40:18,420
A walking God of Wealth.

497
00:40:21,840 --> 00:40:22,380
Wait.

498
00:40:23,990 --> 00:40:26,050
Did you see me as a cash cow from the very start?

499
00:40:26,670 --> 00:40:27,610
Never!

500
00:40:28,440 --> 00:40:30,570
I've always treated Your Highness with sincerity.

501
00:40:36,320 --> 00:40:37,220
Eat more, go on.

502
00:40:37,840 --> 00:40:38,970
Try this dish.

503
00:40:39,280 --> 00:40:40,970
Lifei, you're truly skilled at cooking.

504
00:40:40,990 --> 00:40:42,300
- Here. - This radish tastes incredible.

505
00:40:42,320 --> 00:40:43,940
Xiuyuan, tasty. Have a bowl first.

506
00:40:44,360 --> 00:40:46,450
This one's delicious too, Changyue.

507
00:40:46,760 --> 00:40:48,170
Tongzhou, let me serve you another bowl.

508
00:40:48,400 --> 00:40:49,010
Have some too.

509
00:40:53,470 --> 00:40:55,260
Only the power of a fox spirit can save him.

510
00:40:56,110 --> 00:40:57,340
The sooner you catch the fox spirit,

511
00:40:57,550 --> 00:40:59,220
the sooner you'll see Mr. Lu.

512
00:40:59,960 --> 00:41:02,050
A person who treats you faithfully amid hardship

513
00:41:02,400 --> 00:41:04,820
and stands by you unto death surpasses your family.

514
00:41:05,190 --> 00:41:05,860
Right.

515
00:41:06,510 --> 00:41:09,340
From this day on, we are family.

516
00:41:17,320 --> 00:41:17,970
Xiuyuan.

517
00:41:19,550 --> 00:41:20,260
Xiuyuan!

518
00:41:23,470 --> 00:41:23,970
Look here.

519
00:41:24,760 --> 00:41:27,220
Listen, this rabbit stole my radishes.

520
00:41:27,320 --> 00:41:28,490
I tricked it down at last.

521
00:41:28,840 --> 00:41:30,780
Steal again, and I'll stew you with radishes!

522
00:41:38,360 --> 00:41:40,450
I just called you several times, and you didn't answer.

523
00:41:41,840 --> 00:41:42,970
Got something on your mind?

524
00:42:38,200 --> 00:42:38,450
[The Eternal Fragrance]

525
00:42:38,450 --> 00:42:40,720
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel,
The Eternal Fragrance]

526
00:42:50,620 --> 00:42:53,900
♪Nightmares rage before the dawn♪

527
00:42:54,020 --> 00:42:57,540
♪Merely ephemeral blooms that fade in a blink♪

528
00:42:57,740 --> 00:43:02,740
♪Crushed ten thousand times, yet we embrace the pain♪

529
00:43:02,940 --> 00:43:06,580
♪Heaven sent us here, no ordinary youths♪

530
00:43:06,740 --> 00:43:09,860
♪Through calamities, we do not hold back♪

531
00:43:10,020 --> 00:43:16,140
♪With righteous faith, we seal away the perils of the world♪

532
00:43:17,060 --> 00:43:21,420
♪All the way from the foot of the mountain to the peak♪

533
00:43:21,700 --> 00:43:24,340
♪I've passed through cliffs of blades and seas of fire♪

534
00:43:24,500 --> 00:43:27,540
♪Breaking the seal against thousands, returning in glory♪

535
00:43:27,620 --> 00:43:30,820
♪The ones who make it are the chosen ones♪

536
00:43:30,940 --> 00:43:34,060
♪With you, beneath the stars, the sun and moon♪

537
00:43:34,220 --> 00:43:37,100
♪This unquenchable fervor is a wonder to behold♪

538
00:43:37,140 --> 00:43:40,260
♪One final battle, we charge ahead♪

539
00:43:40,340 --> 00:43:44,140
♪The path of light is not far away♪

540
